parameters:
Henchman: Gyahaha! This mascot guy suits being a punching
bag more than a boss, doesn't he? At 100 yen a pop, it's
quite the moneymaker!
Shark Broccoli: P-please... don't hit me...

Henchman: I've got a great idea! Let's hang this guy upside
down at the entrance of the station! Like that shark statue
at the theme park, and charge 100 yen per commemorative
photo.

Henchman: Nice, it'll become a new landmark of Profit City!
Should I go buy some rope from the home center...

Underling: Don't mess with me! You octopus bastard!! How
dare you do such a thing to the great boss!!
Memimi: Hey, stop, you mustn't hit anyone...!

Henchman: Ah-ah, I got hurt, it's really painful! You're
gonna have to make this right...

Shark Broccoli: W-wait... Hitting a superior is a serious
issue, but ultimately, it was done in an attempt to protect
me. I should take responsibility...

Memimi: Please wait, Boss-sama!! It's my fault for not being
able to stop my subordinate! I should take responsibility...

Henchman: Then let Shark Duke take responsibility. As
punishment, instead of Shark Broccoli, we'll hang you naked
at the station!

Memimi: ...Just as I wish... As someone who stands above
others, I must face the consequences... Being hung naked at
the station is nothing, totally cheap... Ufufu...
*muttering*
